Subject: unable to login
Description: We are a partner. When we login with account mauro.vecchiato@sanmarcogroup.it, it asks to reset password. After we insert the password (the one just used to login) we got error "The password provided is different from the existing password." How can we access the online console?
What_We_Know__c: The customer could not access their EPP Server UI with their credentials.  We performed a password reset procedure to allow the customer to login with the root administrator again with the default password.
Next_Steps__c: Issue resolved in remote session. Case can be closed.
Solution_Comment__c: The customer could not access their EPP Server UI with their credentials.  We performed a password reset procedure to allow the customer to login with the root administrator again with the default password.  Case closed.
